New Day Cdre Center Opens
By holly~ acquire
Since a woman's place cannon always
be in the home, a day care center has
been opened to provide Grinnell preIehoolers with a place to stay while their
mothers are out on such undomestic current as working or going back to school.
The Grinnell Community Day Caro
Center, in operation [or only two weeks,
l5 located in the basement of the First
United Presbyterian Church at 1015 birth
Avenue, Having a capacity oi twenty
children, from three to six years old, the
